Texts.Eng:
Seasoned chicken canned after some grilling. Should be skewered like a kebab. Comes from a pre-Protectorate nation of Earth that Letheia's Hylotl masters don't like to talk about. That's why Letheia's indentured human resources tend to covet it like contraband. Perhaps this is seized judiciously to avoid implications that aliens like the Hylotl had been manipulating things on Earth long before the Protectorate was formed...
^orange;Type: Cooked Meat^reset;
